spec_data.Name: python-humanize
spec_data.Description:
This modest package contains various common humanization utilities, like turning
a number into a fuzzy human readable duration ('3 minutes ago') or into a human
readable size or throughput.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 01:24:33 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Turns dates in to human readable format, e.g '3 minutes ago'
